{
  "id": "69da0bf1686f448faa2a99c0",
  "title": "Cosenseでホバーカードを実装する",
  "created": 1775897587,
  "updated": 1775965944,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69da0bf1686f448faa2a99c0",
      "text": "Cosenseでホバーカードを実装する",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897587,
      "updated": 1775897662
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0c3e000000000030c4dc",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ed95c0378d313a0c36397e2ed1528241]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897662,
      "updated": 1775897754
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0c9a000000000030c4dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897754,
      "updated": 1775897754
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0c37000000000030c4db",
      "text": "　自分のCosenseには動画のようにリンクをホバーすると概要が見れるといった機能を実装しています。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897655,
      "updated": 1775897781
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0cae000000000030c4df",
      "text": "　ただ、これメンバーごとにJSを埋め込んでるので、他の人には反映されないのが難点…。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897775,
      "updated": 1775897800
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0cc8000000000030c4e0",
      "text": "　\tもし他の人にもデフォルトで実装する方法ご存じの方いらっしゃいましたら教えてください[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897800,
      "updated": 1775897816
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0dbe00000000001ccd14",
      "text": "　\t [ProjectScript]という有料版の機能（たぶん、ソレジャナイと言われそうですが…）[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1775898047,
      "updated": 1775898138
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0c9e000000000030c4de",
      "text": "　　　　なんと…課金しないと実装できないんですね…。[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775897758,
      "updated": 1775898240
    },
    {
      "id": "69da100e0000000000928448",
      "text": "　　　　任意のJSを他者のブラウザで実行可能になってしまうので、ビジネス版以外で使えるようになることはまずないと思います[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1775898628,
      "updated": 1775898725
    },
    {
      "id": "69da10700000000000928449",
      "text": "　　　　 cf. [ProjectCSS]は見た目を無茶苦茶にできるけど任意コード実行まではできないので許容されている",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1775898726,
      "updated": 1775898765
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0fda0000000000928445",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1775898576,
      "updated": 1775898579
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0fde0000000000928446",
      "text": "デザインがかっこいい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1775898580,
      "updated": 1775898587
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0fe50000000000928447",
      "text": " パクっ……参考にして[takker99/ScrapBubble]にも取り入れたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1775898587,
      "updated": 1775898622
    },
    {
      "id": "69da0e7500000000002b495f",
      "text": "　　ありがとうございます！どんどん使ってください！[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775898230,
      "updated": 1775901594
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1b2f0000000000111f0d",
      "text": "　　よかったらぜひ[/TECHSTOCK]覗きに来てください",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901486,
      "updated": 1775901639
    },
    {
      "id": "69da210a0000000000ece16e",
      "text": "　　　[UserCSSがすごいプロジェクト]だ…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1775902986,
      "updated": 1775903032
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1ba90000000000111f0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901609,
      "updated": 1775901609
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c810000000000b4567c",
      "text": "ソースコード",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901825,
      "updated": 1775901828
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c6b0000000000b454d4",
      "text": "code:script.js",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901804,
      "updated": 1775901815
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c790000000000b455a9",
      "text": " // Cosense Hover Card Preview",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455aa",
      "text": "  (() => {",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455ab",
      "text": "    const PROJECT = location.pathname.split('/')[1];",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455ac",
      "text": "    const CACHE = new Map();",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455ad",
      "text": "    let card = null;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455ae",
      "text": "    let hideTimer = null;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455af",
      "text": "    let showTimer = null;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b0",
      "text": "    let currentLink = null;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b1",
      "text": "  ",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b2",
      "text": "    function createCard() {",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b3",
      "text": "      const el = document.createElement('div');",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b4",
      "text": "      el.id = 'hover-card';",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b5",
      "text": "      el.innerHTML = `",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b6",
      "text": "        <div class=\"hc-image\"></div>",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b7",
      "text": "        <div class=\"hc-body\">",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b8",
      "text": "          <div class=\"hc-title\"></div>",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455b9",
      "text": "          <div class=\"hc-desc\"></div>",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455ba",
      "text": "        </div>",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455bb",
      "text": "      `;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455bc",
      "text": "      document.body.appendChild(el);",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455bd",
      "text": "      el.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455be",
      "text": "        clearTimeout(hideTimer);",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455bf",
      "text": "      });",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455c0",
      "text": "      el.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455c1",
      "text": "        scheduleHide();",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455c2",
      "text": "      });",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455c3",
      "text": "      return el;",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1775901818,
      "updated": 1775901818
    },
    {
      "id": "69da1c7a0000000000b455c4",
      "text": "    }",
